*************Suspicious OAuth Token Abuse***************************
 MITRE T1528 â€“ Steal Application Access Token
Type: Threat Hunting â†’ Can become Detection

index=azure_logs sourcetype="o365:audit"
| search Operation="RefreshToken"
| stats dc(src_ip) AS distinct_ips values(src_ip) AS ip_list by user, user_agent
| where distinct_ips > 2

Replace:

index=azure_logs â†’ Your Azure/O365 index

src_ip, user â†’ Use correct field names (may be ipAddress, userPrincipalName





